data.description: Welcome to your dream home, situated on a huge corner lot! From the gorgeous  leaded glass front door to extensive wood-look tile flooring, this place is a sure to please. Two spacious bedrooms greet you at the entrance—both with high ceilings and an abundance of closet space. Straight ahead, a light and airy family room features a stack stone fireplace & built-in for your cherished photos. The kitchen’s a culinary dream: quartz counters, sleek backsplash, terrific island with seating and a walk-in pantry that is massive    The Primary bedroom is a personal oasis that has a bay window with amazing views of the pool and an ensuite that serves as your own sanctuary. This home also has two bonus rooms to use for whatever you desire and an air-conditioned workshop/craft room for your hobbies. Out back finds a backyard paradise: fresh landscaping, heated pool and spa, and a covered patio with pergola that is perfect for BBQs. Come live the good life! Never flooded.
